name: R4B-Parameters-R5-Parameters
title: Concept map to convert a FHIR R4B Parameters into FHIR R5

target.comment: R4B `Parameters` maps as Equivalent to R5 `Parameters`
R4B `Parameters.id` maps as Equivalent to R5 `Parameters.id`

element.display: A set of rules under which this content was created

target.display: A set of rules under which this content was created
target.comment: R4B `Parameters.implicitRules` maps as Equivalent to R5 `Parameters.implicitRules`
R4B `Parameters.language` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `Parameters.language` - language made the binding required (from Preferred) for http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/all-languages|5.0.0
R4B `Parameters.meta` maps as Equivalent to R5 `Parameters.meta`
R4B `Parameters.parameter` maps as Equivalent to R5 `Parameters.parameter`

R4B `Parameters.parameter.extension` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `Parameters.parameter.extension` - extension has change due to type change: R4B `extension` `Extension` maps as RelatedTo for R5 `extension`
R4B `Parameters.parameter.id` maps as Equivalent to R5 `Parameters.parameter.id`

R4B `Parameters.parameter.name` maps as Equivalent to R5 `Parameters.parameter.name`
